.NET Framework 3.5.name: SDK_InputSimulator
.NET Framework 3.5.summary: The VRSimulatorCameraRig prefab is a mock Camera Rig set up that can be used to develop with VRTK without the need for VR Hardware.
.NET Framework 3.5.remarks: Use the mouse and keyboard to move around both play area and hands and interacting with objects without the need of a hmd or VR controls.

methods.name: FindInScene()
methods.summary: The FindInScene method is used to find the VRSimulatorCameraRig GameObject within the current scene.
methods.returns: Returns the found VRSimulatorCameraRig GameObject if it is found. If it is not found then it prints a debug log error.
